This chapter was developed based on [this resource](https://github.com/rstudio/learnr/tree/main/inst/tutorials/ex-setup-r/ex-setup-r.Rmd). The goal is to make sure you have R and Rstudio installed on your computer and make sure you have a folder set up for this class to make your semester go smoother.

__Outline__

This chapter will help you set up your computer to use R. It is for you if you need to:

-   Install R on your computer
-   Install the RStudio IDE
-   Get set up with R projects

You can skip this chapter if you've already done these things.